  "title": "Gardener / Landscape Worker | Sengkang Hospital",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>5.5 Days Per Week | Sunday OFF</strong></li><li><strong>8am-5pm (Mon to Fri) | 8am to 12pm (Sat)</strong></li><li><strong>Gardener | Plant Nurturer | Horticultural & Landscape Worker | Plantation Nursery</strong></li><li><strong>Basic Salary: SGD $1,950 [ Fix ]</strong></li><li><strong>Entitled to Medical Benefits & Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Working location at Sengkang General Hospitals</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Must be<strong> Covid vaccination certified </strong>due to the <u><strong>work environment at hospitals.</strong></u></li><li>Prefer those with <u><strong>basic plantation knowledge and gardener experience.</strong></u></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scopes:</strong></p><ol><li>Weeding and mulching landscape beds</li><li>Trimming small trees, hedges and shrubs</li><li>Removing unwanted, dead or damaged trees</li><li>Planting shrubs, flowers and trees</li><li>Watering gardens, lawns and landscapes</li><li>Grass cutting</li><li>Fertilizing plants</li><li>Monitoring and maintaining plant health</li></ol><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
